TALKING POINT - USAir must refocus , seek alliance . Almost free of its estranged British Airways Plc partner , USAir Group Inc must now confront the difficult task of securing new international partners or face possible takeover pressure , analysts said . Since almost a quarter of USAir ' s equity remains up for grabs , some analysts see USAir emerging as a prime acquisition target . " It certainly moves USAir to the center of the radar screen , " said Tom Schreier , an airline analyst with CS First Boston . 
